We are deeply committed to the health and safety of our community 💚

Please head to the nearest emergency room or urgent can if you are in a high-risk group (over 65, young child, history of breathing disorders like asthma, compromised immune system) and are experiencing symptoms of smoke exposure like chest pain, burning eyes, increased heart rate, and coughing.

Additionally @mutualaidla is providing updates on shelters, free N95 mask distribution, evacuation maps, and other essential resources.

Our West Hollywood location will be closed today and tomorrow but will reopen next week. We remain committed to serving the community, so if you need assistance or guidance, please contact us at care@parsleyhealth.com.
